functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: How old is each of the main cast members of the TV series Girls?
How old is each of the main cast members of the TV series Girls?

The four main cast members in Girls are Lena Dunham, Jemima Kirke, Allison Williams, and Zosia Mamet. Their ages are as follows:

- Lena Dunham is 37 years old (born on 13 May 1986).
- Jemima Kirke is 38 years old (born on 26 April 1985).
- Allison Williams is 35 years old (born on 13 April 1988).
- Zosia Mamet is 35 years old (born on 2 February 1988).
